Privacy Policy — WiFi & Internet Speed Test Pro
Effective Date: March 8, 2026

1. Overview
WiFi & Internet Speed Test Pro ("the App") is operated by Balineni ("we", "us", or "our"). This Privacy Policy explains how the App handles information when you use it. We are committed to protecting your privacy.

2. Information We Do Not Collect
We do not collect, store, transmit, or share any personally identifiable information. The App does not require account creation, login, or registration of any kind.

3. Information Stored Locally on Your Device
The App stores the following data locally on your device only. This data never leaves your device and is never transmitted to us:

Speed test results (download speed, upload speed, ping, jitter, packet loss)
Test timestamps
App preferences and settings

You can delete this data at any time by clearing the App's data in your device settings or by uninstalling the App.

4. Network Usage During Speed Tests
When you run a speed test, the App connects to Cloudflare's speed test servers (speed.cloudflare.com) to measure your internet speed. During this process:

A sample of data is downloaded from and uploaded to Cloudflare's servers solely to measure speed
Your IP address is visible to Cloudflare as part of the standard internet connection process
Cloudflare's own Privacy Policy governs any data they may process: https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/

The App also detects your Internet Service Provider (ISP) name and connection type (WiFi, 4G, 5G) using your device's network APIs. This information is displayed within the App only and is never transmitted to us.

5. No Advertising
The App contains no advertisements and does not use any advertising SDKs or ad networks.

6. No Analytics or Tracking
The App does not use any analytics, crash reporting, or user tracking services. We do not track your usage behavior, session duration, or any in-app actions.

7. No Third-Party SDKs
The App does not integrate any third-party analytics, marketing, or data collection SDKs.

8. Children's Privacy
The App does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13. The App is safe for use by all ages.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the App's Play Store listing. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

